g\" >Spread Happiness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Harvestvale, happiness grows from even the smallest interaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spreading happiness is the goal of every Guild Rookie. Happiness brings growth, enabling you to upgrade your caravan, learn new crafting recipes, and more! If you’re looking for ways to help, there’s always someone in need. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788520/extras/90e86220009fdddbeb2ec7fa1c6d5f13.poster.avif?t=1767858782\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788520/extras/90e86220009fdddbeb2ec7fa1c6d5f13.webm?t=1767858782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Share The Fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break and say “<i>hoyo</i>!” to the local townsfolk and join in on fun activities! Test your stone-skipping skills by the water, or drop a fishing line in a nearby pond. Build connections with local townsfolk by joining games of Hide & Seek or Hopscotch. You can even help cafes with their lunchtime rush! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788520/extras/715a35f029e5d373737c6076cecdfa84.poster.avif?t=1767858782\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788520/extras/715a35f029e5d373737c6076cecdfa84.webm?t=1767858782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fair Game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The annual Whizz Bang Fair is just around the corner, but it’s all gone awry! Help folks along the way as they try to get things ready for the big day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788520/extras/c841402eebd8c6ff43330c1472f9c820.poster.avif?t=1767858782\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788520/extras/c841402eebd8c6ff43330c1472f9c820.webm?t=1767858782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
